Developer Terms of Use
des:
Alexa is making it even easier to find out what's going on at Jubilee Cake Studio. With the Jubilee Cake Studio skill, you can get the list of upcoming workshops, hear what others are saying about Jubilee Cake Studio, and have fun with some of the more playful features.

To get started, just say "Alexa, open Jubilee Cake Studio." Alexa will connect you to Jubilee Cake Studio where you can ask "Who did you vote for in the last election", or tell Jubilee Cake Studio exactly how you feel "Tell Jubilee Cake Studio that I love them."

If you're interested in upcoming workshops, you can ask "Alexa, ask Jubilee Cake Studio about the next workshop". The simply say "next workshop" to hear the next available workshop.

Forget where we are located? Simple ask "Alexa, ask Jubilee Cake Studio for their address." It couldn't be simpler to get directions to our store.

Learn more about Jubilee Cake Studio at http://www.JubileeCakeStudio.com
